---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Collapsible Metal Ramp">

    <main class="main">

    <!-- Page Title -->
    <div class="page-title">
      <div class="breadcrumbs">
        <nav aria-label="breadcrumb">
          <ol class="breadcrumb">
            <li class="breadcrumb-item"><a href="/"><i class="bi bi-house"></i> Home</a></li>
            <li class="breadcrumb-item"><a href="/portfolio">Portfolio</a></li>
            <li class="breadcrumb-item active current">Collapsible Metal Ramp</li>
          </ol>
        </nav>
      </div>

      <div class="container section-title pb-0">
        <h2>Collapsible Metal Ramp</h2>
        <div class="title-shape">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 200 20" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M 0,10 C 40,0 60,20 100,10 C 140,0 160,20 200,10" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
      </div><!-- End Section Title -->
    </div><!-- End Page Title -->

    <!-- Portfolio Details Section -->
    <section id="portfolio-details" class="portfolio-details section">

      <div class="container">

        <div class="row gy-4 g-lg-5">
          <div class="col-lg-6">
            <img src="/assets/img/portfolio/51.webp" class="img-fluid mb-4" alt="" loading="lazy">
            <img src="/assets/img/portfolio/52.webp" class="img-fluid mb-4" alt="" loading="lazy">
            <img src="/assets/img/portfolio/53.webp" class="img-fluid mb-4" alt="" loading="lazy">
            <img src="/assets/img/portfolio/54.webp" class="img-fluid mb-4" alt="" loading="lazy">
            <img src="/assets/img/portfolio/55.webp" class="img-fluid mb-4" alt="" loading="lazy">
          </div>

          <div class="col-lg-6">

            <div class="position-sticky" style="top: 40px">

              <div class="portfolio-description">
                <h2>Overview</h2>
                <p>
                  Collapsible wheelchair ramp designed for safe load transfer and compact storage, with a multi-panel folding structure and full fabrication-ready technical documentation.
                </p>

                <div class="portfolio-info mt-5">
                  <h2>Specifications</h2>
                  <ul>
                    <li><strong>Load Capacity:</strong> ~100 kg</li>
                    <li><strong>Structure:</strong> 4-panel folding ramp with hinge mechanism</li>
                    <li><strong>Total Length (open):</strong> ~36 in</li>
                    <li><strong>Weight:</strong> ~79 lb total assembly</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>

                <h2>Materials</h2>
                <p>
                  <ul>
                    <li>Ramp Panels: 7075-T6 Aluminum</li>
                    <li>Rails & Curbs: 6061-T6 Aluminum</li>
                    <li>Hinges & Pins: AISI 304 Stainless Steel</li>
                    <li>Surface: Silicon rubber non-slip layer</li>
                  </ul>
                </p>

                <h2>Design Approach</h2>
                <p>
                  The ramp was designed as a modular multi-panel system connected via piano hinges, enabling folding into a compact form while maintaining structural continuity under load.
                  <br><br>
                  Cross-support members and side curbs were integrated to improve stiffness and ensure safe wheel guidance during operation.
                </p>

                <h2>Key Features</h2>
                <p>
                  <ul>
                    <li>Multi-panel folding mechanism for compact storage</li>
                    <li>Non-slip surface for safe wheelchair operation</li>
                    <li>Side curbs and rails for wheel alignment and safety</li>
                    <li>Fully detailed BOM and fabrication drawings for manufacturing</li>
                  </ul>
                </p>

                <h2>Deliverables</h2>
                <p>
                  <ul>
                    <li>Complete 2D engineering drawing set (10 sheets)</li>
                    <li>Full BOM with materials and quantities</li>
                    <li>Assembly definition with exploded and folded configurations</li>
                  </ul>
                </p>

                <h2>Outcome</h2>
                <p>
                  Delivered a fabrication-ready ramp system combining structural integrity, portability, and user safety, supported by complete technical documentation for manufacturing.
                </p>

              </div>

              <div class="portfolio-info mt-5">
                <h3>Project information</h3>
                <ul>
                  <li><strong>Category</strong> Independent Project</li>
                  <li><strong>Project date</strong> October, 2026</li>
                  <li><strong>Project URL</strong> <a href="https://grabcad.com/library/collapsible-metal-ramp-1" target="_blank">https://grabcad.com/library/collapsible-metal-ramp-1</a></li>
                  <li><strong>Workflow Recording</strong> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLp7dj9uy6_743qUUuPx1rnmUFPp4ITwj0">YouTube Playlist</a></li>
                  <li><a href="https://grabcad.com/library/collapsible-metal-ramp-1" class="btn-visit align-self-start" target="_blank">Download CAD Files</a></li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>

          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

    </section><!-- /Portfolio Details Section -->

    </main>

</BaseLayout>



